Pin connections for MCP4151.

Three 10kohm devices are required - one for each axis, connected as follows:

1 -CS (Chip Select) - Nano Pin 14/15/16 for X/Y/Z axis respectively
2 - SCK (Clock) - Nano Pin 13 (SCK) for all devices
3 - SDI/SDO (Serial) - Nano Pin 11 (MOSI) for all devices
4 - GND (0V)
5 - GND (0v)
6 - Wiper out - Connect to the X/Y/Z joystick input on your RAMPs/3D printer controller
7 - VCC (5v)
8 - VCC (5v)
